emuInput.TitMainTitle: Carolyn Waters, Billy House, Ruth Ann Wheeler, Grant Farmer, Suzanne Jones, Gene Daryle Hill, Bonnie Waters, and Marva Acie seated at round table, with Morris Fountain Sr. standing on right in back, in Loendi Club for FROGS Teenage Dance Party
emuInput.CatDescriptText: Cutline of image published in Pittsburgh Courier newspaper, July 30, 1960, pg. 20 reads: "Sitting One Out-Enjoying a breather between dances at the Frogs' teen-age party was the above group. Seated, clockwise, are Carolyn Waters, McKeesport; Billy House (face hidden behind Carolyn) of Elizabeth; Ruth Ann Wheeler, Monessen; Grant Farmer, Rochester; Suzanne Jones, McKeesport; Gene Daryle Hill, Monessen; Bonnie Waters and Marva Acie, both of McKeesport.-Harris Photo."
